The '''''Star Traveler''''' was a [[Light freighter/Legends|light freighter]] that was owned and operated by the [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Renna Strego]]. It accompanied [[Roa]]'s [[Lwyll (Redthorn-class)|''Lwyll'']] during the [[Battle of Nar Shaddaa (4 BBY)|Battle of Nar Shaddaa]].

